  "title": "✈️ (TRAVEL PERK) BRAND & SALES ASSOCIATE ✈️",
  "description": "<h2>🗣️✈️ Love meeting people AND love travelling?</h2><p>Why not do both in your full-time job? Join our team and <strong>level up your communication skills</strong>, <strong>earn</strong> <strong>great income,</strong> and <strong>travel across Asia</strong> to learn from top-performing professionals.</p><p><br /></p><h3>✅ What You’ll Do</h3><ul><li>Represent brands at events & pop-ups</li><li>Engage customers face-to-face</li><li>Work with teams across different countries</li><li>Pick up real-world sales & people skills</li></ul><p><br /></p><h3>✈️ Why You’ll Love It</h3><ul><li>Regional travel for training & networking</li><li>Young, energetic team culture</li><li>Fast progression into leadership roles</li><li>No experience needed — full training provided</li></ul><p><br /></p><h3>👀 You’re Perfect If You…</h3><ul><li>Are excited to explore new place</li><li>Aged 18-29</li><li>Want to grow confidence & communication skills</li><li>Love hands-on</li><li>Are adaptable, driven, and people-oriented</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>📩 <strong>Ready to work, learn, grow — and see the world? Apply now!</strong></p>",
